    • Method Detail

      • setupDescriptionModifiers

        protected abstract void setupDescriptionModifiers()
        Abstract method used to configure the modifiers of an object based on object-specific rules. The implementation of this method should call addDescriptionModifier(ModifierName, String), clearDescriptionModifiers(), and removeDescriptionModifier(ModifierName) to manage the modifiers.

      • getDescription

        public java.lang.String getDescription()
        Any class which extends edu.cscc.javaadventure.JAObject must implement setupModifiers This function asks the object to generate a collection of description modifiers based on its state (such as open or closed, lit or unlit, etc). The getDescription method then appends those description modifiers to the base description, generating a complete description of the object.
        Returns:
        The description based on all modifiers.
